  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flip Flop XL</strong> is a fun, addictive, and endlessly challenging game that tests your timing and skill. Press, hold, and release to crouch, jump, and perform incredible flips. Land perfectly to rack up points, chain your flips, and set new high scores to outflip your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why You'll Love Flip Flop XL:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌀 <strong>Endless Fun:</strong> A relaxing yet rewarding flipping challenge that keeps you coming back for \"just one more try.\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Stylish Minimalist Graphics:</strong> Cute and quirky characters with tons of personality.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Simple One-Tap Controls:</strong> Easy to learn, impossible to master, perfect for all ages!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>Compete with Friends:</strong> Break records and climb the leaderboards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎁 <strong>Unlock Colors & Accessories:</strong> Customize your flippers with vibrant colors, wacky hats, glasses, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're a casual player looking for quick fun or a pro aiming for the perfect flip streak, <strong>Flip Flop XL</strong> delivers a uniquely satisfying experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A variety of unlockable colors and accessories</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/2e1ff680ed2de0e42411c00b15897ff7.poster.avif?t=1745903767\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/2e1ff680ed2de0e42411c00b15897ff7.webm?t=1745903767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/2e1ff680ed2de0e42411c00b15897ff7.mp4?t=1745903767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A surprisingly minor upgrade system (does that make this a rogue-lite?)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/5623216eb0cffaec200ec49acc5a5dce.poster.avif?t=1745903767\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/5623216eb0cffaec200ec49acc5a5dce.webm?t=1745903767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/5623216eb0cffaec200ec49acc5a5dce.mp4?t=1745903767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Connect to Twitch (optional)  and let chat flip with you!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/88fccc5df8d091004dd8754d0a306839.poster.avif?t=1745903767\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/88fccc5df8d091004dd8754d0a306839.webm?t=1745903767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/88fccc5df8d091004dd8754d0a306839.mp4?t=1745903767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Or let chat play alone and write on clouds, perfect for BRB or Just Chatting</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/cd6c62b4f8786ff9ee34052be034e3b5.poster.avif?t=1745903767\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/cd6c62b4f8786ff9ee34052be034e3b5.webm?t=1745903767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298150/extras/cd6c62b4f8786ff9ee34052be034e3b5.mp4?t=1745903767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
